                <div class="columns w-row">
                    <div class="column column-1 w-col w-col-2">

                    </div>
                    <div class="column column-1 w-col w-col-8">
                        <div class="page-text">
                            <p style="font-size: 1.0rem; line-height: 1.8; color: #1a1a1a; text-align: left;">
                                Anne Huntington operates through a dual structure designed to sustain independent research while delivering commercial and applied products. The Research and Consulting Division focuses on defense and scientific consulting, systems R&D and contracting, operating through subcontracts, retainers, and R&D collaborations via established trust networks.
                            </p>
                            <p style="font-size: 1.0rem; line-height: 1.8; color: #1a1a1a; margin-top: 1rem; text-align: left;">
                                Huntington Applied serves as the laboratory's enabling technology arm, developing forecasting and intelligence tools through app sales, licensing, and strategic partnerships with a public-facing, modern scientific approach. This closed-loop ecosystem enables Anne Huntington to generate proprietary methods and trust networks while Huntington Applied deploys those methods commercially, with revenue from both sustaining research independence. We work with partners who share our values and commitment to advancing knowledge—building relationships through demonstrated competence and mission alignment.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
