                    </div>
                    <div class="column column-1 w-col w-col-8">
                        <div class="page-text">
                            <p style="font-size: 1.0rem; line-height: 1.8; color: #1a1a1a; text-align: left;">
                                Anne Huntington delivers advanced consulting and R&D in RF technology, intelligence systems, and scientific infrastructure—combining deep physical science with modern computational intelligence. Our core capabilities include multiphysics simulation intelligence, defense technology integration, RF and sensing systems, device design and optimization, and research software architecture.
                            </p>
                            <p style="font-size: 1.0rem; line-height: 1.8; color: #1a1a1a; margin-top: 1rem; text-align: left;">
                                We provide precision consulting across multiple domains through speed without bureaucracy and cross-domain synthesis proven in operational environments. Our work includes technical subcontracts with defined deliverables, advisory retainers for strategic consulting, joint research collaborations with institutions, and system audits providing comprehensive integrity reviews.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    <script src="https://d3e54v103j8qbb.cloudfront.net/js/jquery-3.5.1.min.dc5e7f18c8.js?site=601b20f503b357c9c3e3c9a6"
        type="text/javascript" integrity="sha256-9/aliU8dGd2tb6OSsuzixeV4y/faTqgFtohetphbbj0=" crossorigin="anonymous">
